Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:09.78,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I have a slight concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:13.90,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take a small number \Nfrom our forces to eliminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:18.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have any need of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:24.13,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama, head to safety in the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.24,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Do not release the children's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:33.59,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are master and servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.68,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look just like his.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:45.45,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wilhelm-san, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.97,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.75,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot use such means, such tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:23.14,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,to make light of me and of my devotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is some crappy game where, \Nonce as you're caught, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We must be crazy to entrust our lives to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,you and me both!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.43,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My body is slowly getting used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.68,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we speed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:46.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Don't worry, I'll keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:55.66,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:58.32,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, impossible, impossible, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.00,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.50,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why? How can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:07.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was loved! I am loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.98,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,By the witch, the witch, the witch, the witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.73,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.85,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's time that I killed you for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.74,Default - italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Al Clauseria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.40,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.20,Default - italics,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ul Dona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Burn, fighting spirit! Howl, magic ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When I get serious, I can pitch over 120 km/h!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.61,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.78,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You lost because you belittled \Nhim as powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:08.14,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My blade, of all six elements together, \Nwill slice your very soul apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.75,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter to the rainbow's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.83,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let it end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.11,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I have been nothing but diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.34,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The witch's love bathes my entire body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius, undo Nect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.47,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... My brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just tremble while you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play along with you, just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,To the witch that you've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can Return by Death to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.01,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.72,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:08.92,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,For your love, your merciful love, \Nyour affectionate love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.31,Default,Satella,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.83,Default,Satella,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.94,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This... cannot... be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:31.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared to keep\Ntrying until you left me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:35.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but you gave up after one go? \NHow cowardly can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.88,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will end you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.92,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.30,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:51.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,After everything I've done for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:56.95,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Witch! Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You were Sloth, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.70,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, let us hurry back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.82,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Felis just contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.47,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:40.84,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,The magic stones of fire that were\Nin the merchants' inventory are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.33,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,We unloaded all our cargo so we \Ncould transport the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.85,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,But the magic stones of fire are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:54.18,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Someone left the stones on board \Nwhen they loaded the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.11,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,It was Ketty-san's carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:06:00.23,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,There are enough magic stones to \Neasily blow away a small village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:10.14,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Ketty's carriage is taking Emilia-sama \Nand the children to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.36,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.09,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.49,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My poor man's tendency to use \Nanything at hand backfired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We have verified that no spell \Nwas used to set a trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:47.31,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but if something were physically \Nrigged in the carriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, could a ground dragon catch up to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.29,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Once they leave the Mathers domain \Nand get on the Lifaus Highway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.36,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be hard to catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That still wasn't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even after all that, I still can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.61,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,May I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.10,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm actually\Nin a desperate position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.56,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,If you would accept a trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.64,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to catch up to\Nthe carriage that lef—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything I can do, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.83,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I like a man who can decide \Nquickly, Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.91,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send Ia with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:27.05,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could accompany you myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.01,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.66,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,With all those injuries, how could \Nyou help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.97,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,And your mana's {\i1}nyot{\i0} restored yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is over, we'll celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to invite you, so don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.68,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.90,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.67,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than take this road,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.24,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,it's faster to go through\Nthe glade to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.93,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,It's the shortest way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your "soul of language" \Ndivine protection is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.91,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I had a hard time learning to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:06.75,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can hear all creatures' voices, \Nfrom ground dragons to insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But if we choose our path \Nbased on what they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,this shortcut will work, and catching up \Nto Emilia and the kids will be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.09,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:24.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're seriously gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.09,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? I feel a wind hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.17,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, even I had no idea \NI was capable of this—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.37,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,The trees are so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:43.16,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,The birds and bugs began to make \Na lot of noise, and then just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:46.94,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Something... Something is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:58.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Faster, Otto! Don't get\Ncaught, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.41,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:07.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just how persistent are you, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.21,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.66,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My flesh body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.04,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That old man just ran into \Nsomeone behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.63,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.88,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.92,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:39.09,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,But the old man's power is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.12,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you and I won't be needed this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.91,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Taking physical form without \Nreason drains mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.46,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't want these \Nkids ending up their toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:50.59,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If we could hide everyone's \Nfear behind your cuteness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.62,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I think that could work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.24,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You say some scary things, my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.33,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.58,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.87,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,W-We made a promise, so this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.22,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.58,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,That we wouldn't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.31,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,Because if we aren't with you, \Nyou'll do something crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.43,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll worry if someone doesn't watch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:23.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about me? Who told you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.80,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! We can't tell—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.83,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.37,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.13,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,He said you get lonely easily, \Nso he was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.65,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.60,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we weren't supposed to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.24,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.76,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, is something \Ncoming up behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just some big, black animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:50.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It has a wild voice and a scary face, \Nso you're better off not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.60,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Those things make me all the more curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Just drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it bites me, it'll munch on you next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.80,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:03.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have \Nto play the last level?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What about you is slothful now, \Nyou uselessly hard worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.95,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Witch! Satella! Give me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.05,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't love you or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:15.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Love! Love! Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:17.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In what kind of rom-com does someone \Ntry to squash their love's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Satella! Satella! Satella!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I am your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:27.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I absolutely won't let you \Nget to the kid in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:31.48,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, you care about me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to make myself look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:40.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.58,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, we're leaving the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:49.97,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.33,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Love... Love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.98,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Love alone is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take you with me to where Emilia is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna need your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius Euclius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.35,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rental Goa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:24.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.02,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.38,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.77,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Relinquish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to enter my body, \Nyou're just gonna get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.10,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The witch... Satella... Satella!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:43.50,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten a single moment \Nof the things you did for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.37,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you've forgotten, I'll... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.89,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With all of my diligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.77,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll part with my slothful self, \Nto repay your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you had stayed a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You might have beaten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.12,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Satella...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:17.76,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I... will not... I won't... let it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.06,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.09,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:57.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This time, stay asleep forever, Betelgeuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:58.90,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wilhelm-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:08.82,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Emilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.79,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.50,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Go straight, toward the great tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.92,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance to repay my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:28.88,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Who can stand in the way of a man \Non his way to see a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.94,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.01,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,That's the carriage with the refugees!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.53,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.26,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking about Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.14,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.51,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.30,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If Subaru's really leading the army,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.27,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,lots of things would make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.39,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Like why Ram didn't argue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.48,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,and why the villagers agreed to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.40,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.51,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,After all the pain and suffering \Nhe went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.45,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,After I made him look so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.35,Default - italics,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.58,Default - italics,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Lia, something is coming up behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.58,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this reunion was sudden. \NSo that's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.09,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:01.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.28,Default - flashback,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.27,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,For saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.69,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.30,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.79,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:56.82,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that witch lady coming\Nto grab my heart again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.92,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel too bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.09,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:06.44,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. I can hear, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:13.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying down, and Emilia is kneeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:18.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And considering our distance and the \Nheavenly sensation under my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go through all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is on my lap. It isn't \Nuncomfortable, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know of no finer, more divine pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:30.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:34.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask how things turned out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who wants to ask what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is Patrasche okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:46.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become the wind \Nwith that little guy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty burned,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Felis is looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Felis joined us, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have I been out for a pretty long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.33,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,About an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everyone's together now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:07.01,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Julius, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.75,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to see you two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was for reasons bluer than the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and taller than the seas, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I finally made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:37.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I was having a really long dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.42,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A good dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A good reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you asked me why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why I saved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,why I try so hard at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:07.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And you said it was because I saved you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:12.24,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't done anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.11,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.79,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's always saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I never could do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:24.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you got yourself hurt, \Nand said it was for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was messed up back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking only of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was all for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:37.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,when I was really just drunk on \Nthe idea of doing it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:42.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I had it in my head that if I \Nsaid that, you'd accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.00,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:45.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I used you for my own self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:53.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you said back then was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I wasn't wrong about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:08.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,517)}I honestly mean that. It's no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:11.45,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:17.35,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:21.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to be your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.38,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a half-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:36.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:40.21,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a silver-haired half-elf,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and many people hate me because \NI look like the witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,They despise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:48.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,They absolutely detest me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are all blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:55.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much experience with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:57.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:01.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm naïve and not very worldly, so I \Nsay strange things sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason I want to be the kingdom's \Nruler is really, really selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what you think of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:16.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I really love you! Like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:18.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hold your hand all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:24.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you name ten things\Nyou hate about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:27.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say two thousand things I love about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:32.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:36.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,special treatment I want to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:44.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've received special \Ntreatment that made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.31,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why two thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:57.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Because a hundredfold isn't enough \Nto express how I feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:23:59.37,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:07.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I never even imagined I'd see the day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that someone told me they loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:13.09,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:18.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You've told me so many of your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:22.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:24.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stress over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:26.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not demanding an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:30.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I'm concerned, it's written in \Nstone that you'll give me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.42,0:24:32.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be a positive one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.61,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.09,0:24:41.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,For me... For someone like me to be \Ngiven such happiness all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:44.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,To be so overjoyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually feel like it's indulgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.09,0:24:49.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it is. Go on and be indulgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:52.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can never have too much happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:55.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you have so much that it overflows, \Nyou can always share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.69,0:25:01.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time, Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:06.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time and slowly, \Nsteadily fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.56,0:25:12.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, so I can walk by your side. \NSo you'll fall head over heels for me.
